race.description: Affinity Roofing New England Showcase Mdn Hcp
race.comment: STUCK IN THE GORGE (3) improving gelding who gets out to his right trip today. Failed to sprint with them in the straight when a plugging fifth over 1450m at Muswellbrook in the soft (6) going. Gets the right run again in this easier contest. Go close. LONE STAR DREAM (2) returned from a very lengthy break with an encouraging third over 1500m at Port Macquarie. Savaged the line on that occasion and gets weight relief from the low draw. Sure to be thereabouts. RUFUS ATTICUS (8) deep into the prep and back in trip when a plodding sixth over 1400m at Inverell. Will go back from the draw and can run into the minor money from the awkward draw. TAKETHEMONEYANDRUN (1) consistent gelding due for a change of luck. Chased hard with the 58kg from the low draw when second over 1600m at Gilgandra. Stays in the mix.
